WEBVTT

00:05:29.768 --> 00:05:30.918
Empty.

00:05:31.371 --> 00:05:32.529
It was just sad.

00:05:32.553 --> 00:05:33.726
AG: Ouch.

00:05:33.750 --> 00:05:36.219
JW: So I thought, that's it,
that's the end of me,

00:05:36.243 --> 00:05:39.653
I'll have "The Iron Giant"
on my resume and nothing more.

00:05:40.038 --> 00:05:42.149
AG: The film failed commercially.

00:05:42.173 --> 00:05:43.982
But it was wildly original.

00:05:44.006 --> 00:05:46.585
And the leaders at Pixar
saw potential there.

00:05:46.609 --> 00:05:51.260
So Brad Bird and John Walker got the call
from two of the studio's cofounders,

00:05:51.284 --> 00:05:53.609
Ed Catmull and Steve Jobs.

00:05:53.633 --> 00:05:54.823
JW: They go, you know,

00:05:54.847 --> 00:05:57.067
"We'll bring this bacteria in
from the outside

00:05:57.091 --> 00:05:59.447
and see if it grows
in the petri dish," you know.

00:05:59.471 --> 00:06:04.034
BB: They were actively choosing
a guy to come up